WEBVTT

00:00.400 --> 00:02.835
♪♪

00:04.037 --> 00:07.339
<i> ♪ Welcome to my wicked world ♪</i>

00:07.374 --> 00:09.108
<i> ♪ Wicked world ♪</i>

00:13.380 --> 00:14.513
Well, hello.

00:14.548 --> 00:17.082
-Hey, Audrey.
-Save your sarcasm, Mal,

00:17.117 --> 00:18.984
and save the whole
"I choose good" act

00:19.019 --> 00:20.752
because we know
you've been faking it.

00:20.787 --> 00:22.654
-You've been evil all along!
-(door opens)

00:22.689 --> 00:24.923
Whoa, whoa, whoa.
Accusations are flying

00:24.958 --> 00:26.258
faster than Aladdin in here.

00:26.293 --> 00:28.226
And you don't want to
let frown lines spoil

00:28.261 --> 00:30.328
that beautiful face, do you?

00:30.363 --> 00:32.330
Audrey, we VKs
may be a lot of things,

00:32.365 --> 00:33.765
but we're not fakers.

00:33.800 --> 00:35.000
Just admit it.

00:35.035 --> 00:36.935
You're furious
about not getting a jewel

00:36.970 --> 00:38.670
and you're 100% evil!

00:38.705 --> 00:40.405
You're wrong.
Mal is our friend.

00:40.440 --> 00:44.242
-We have been planning
this song and dance for ages!
-(all arguing)

00:44.277 --> 00:45.944
Stop.

00:45.979 --> 00:47.212
Stop!

00:49.216 --> 00:51.083
"Bicker, holler,
squabble and squawk,

00:51.118 --> 00:52.885
"twist their words
when next they talk!"

00:54.988 --> 00:56.588
In trouble big you are!

00:56.623 --> 00:57.689
Huh?

00:57.724 --> 00:59.357
What now happening is?

00:59.392 --> 01:01.293
Voices are she's bewitched!

01:01.328 --> 01:03.795
Deserve you what get you. Hey!

01:03.830 --> 01:05.931
Okay, okay,
things got a little heated.

01:05.966 --> 01:07.799
We all said things
that didn't make any sense,

01:07.834 --> 01:09.901
but I'm sure
if we ask nicely,

01:09.936 --> 01:11.703
Mal will take it all back.

01:11.738 --> 01:13.172
-Right, Mal?
-Wrong.

01:14.174 --> 01:16.241
♪ I carry on like a princess ♪

01:16.276 --> 01:18.977
♪ But man,
I've got 'em fooled ♪

01:19.012 --> 01:20.812
♪ 'Cause underneath
my business ♪

01:20.847 --> 01:24.316
♪ I am cold,
I'm hard, I'm cruel ♪

01:24.351 --> 01:26.551
♪ Never gonna put
a spell on me ♪

01:26.586 --> 01:29.287
♪ Never ever gonna
bring me back ♪

01:29.322 --> 01:32.757
♪ Never gonna make me
be something I'm not ♪

01:32.792 --> 01:35.293
♪ Because I'm evil ♪

01:35.328 --> 01:36.895
♪ Tell the people ♪

01:36.930 --> 01:39.298
♪ I'm evil ♪

01:40.300 --> 01:42.234
(all exclaiming)

01:42.269 --> 01:43.401
Ally:
What the hare?

01:43.436 --> 01:45.137
Anyone pizza like?

01:45.172 --> 01:46.738
-Here's face in your pie!
-Gross!

01:46.773 --> 01:48.507
-(yelps)
-Sorry so I'm.

01:48.542 --> 01:49.842
(laughs) Oh!

01:51.144 --> 01:52.310
Not bad.

01:52.345 --> 01:54.446
Hey! Eating cures the spell.

01:54.481 --> 01:55.413
Dig in.

01:55.448 --> 01:58.116
-All: Mm!
-That's it!

01:58.151 --> 01:59.484
As chairman of every committee,

01:59.519 --> 02:01.786
I hereby banish you
from the Jewel-bilee.

02:01.821 --> 02:03.288
-(gasps)
-Audrey: And if I had the power,

02:03.323 --> 02:05.323
I would banish you
from Auradon.

02:05.358 --> 02:07.325
Oh, that's okay, Audrey.

02:07.360 --> 02:09.628
♪ Because I'm evil ♪

02:09.663 --> 02:11.296
♪ Feels good to be bad ♪

02:11.331 --> 02:14.432
(chuckles)
♪ So good to be bad ♪

02:14.467 --> 02:16.168
What is going on?

02:18.038 --> 02:19.304
This isn't Mal.

02:19.339 --> 02:21.306
Why is she acting like this?

02:21.341 --> 02:23.642
"Window, window paper-thin,

02:23.677 --> 02:25.043
"open up,
I'm going in."

02:28.515 --> 02:29.781
This is bad.

02:29.816 --> 02:31.416
This is really bad.
